{
  "stem": "3382.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the class of [LAUGHS] geographers, you know, who are studying for geography, nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Here I am.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] accidentally was a spa, a Le Mans spa, south of Odessa where we used to go every single year from Odessa summertime.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember, you know, there every single in detail.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- so he looked at me, then goes the very same thing, you know, [LAUGHS] [POINTS] round with finger, puts it on the atlas.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what had he had to hit?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had to hit Znamenka in Ukraine, on the same page.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I knew also.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then he went to other pages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And similarly, I knew everything-- whatever he did, [LAUGHS] whatever he asked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After-- then, after the end of the class, I saw that he spoke to his assistant, Dr.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Rewenska, Wanda Rewenska.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she came up to me, asked me, what-- where do I study, what do I study, whether I would like to be-- transfer myself to geography.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would facilitate everything, and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, what do geographers can do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Geography is my subject I love, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I read adventure stories, whatever or not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had an atlas, which my stepfather presented when I was bar mitzvahed, a Russian atlas.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I thought-- so she told me if you want to do it, so you have to take this course, this course, this course, and that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I decided, let's take it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wasn't sure whether I would take strict biology, or I will go to zoology and whatever else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is how I started geography.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then I had to drop out because-- you know that 1929 crisis, which was so terrible in the United States was even more terrible in Poland.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
